{"id":1586,"date":"2023-02-28T14:50:54","date_gmt":"2023-02-28T19:50:54","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/staging.cegepsl.qc.ca\/?post_type=professeur&#038;p=1586"},"modified":"2023-06-12T12:04:33","modified_gmt":"2023-06-12T16:04:33","slug":"mouncef-benmimoune","status":"publish","type":"professeur","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/equipe\/mouncef-benmimoune\/","title":{"rendered":"Mouncef Benmimoune"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Je suis un expert en technologie de l&rsquo;information et des communications et mon domaine d&rsquo;expertise couvre plusieurs disciplines telles que l&rsquo;informatique, les t\u00e9l\u00e9communications et l&rsquo;\u00e9lectronique. J&rsquo;ai obtenu un dipl\u00f4me d&rsquo;ing\u00e9nieur en \u00e9lectronique de l&rsquo;USTHB, ainsi qu&rsquo;un dipl\u00f4me de Magister en syst\u00e8mes radiofr\u00e9quences et microondes. J&rsquo;ai \u00e9galement obtenu un doctorat en g\u00e9nie \u00e9lectrique (t\u00e9l\u00e9communication) de l&rsquo;UQTR en 2013. J&rsquo;ai occup\u00e9 le poste de chercheur invit\u00e9 \u00e0 Imperial College London et \u00e0 l&rsquo;\u00e9cole d&rsquo;ing\u00e9nieurs fran\u00e7aise EURECOM. J&rsquo;ai publi\u00e9 plusieurs articles scientifiques sur la technologie de l&rsquo;information dans des conf\u00e9rences et des revues de renom, et j&rsquo;enseigne actuellement \u00e0 Polytechnique Montr\u00e9al et \u00e0 l&rsquo;UQAM.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1587,"template":"","categorie-equipe":[202],"departement-equipe":[281],"specialite-equipe":[],"etiquette-interne":[],"class_list":["post-1586","professeur","type-professeur","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","categorie-equipe-personnel-enseignant","departement-equipe-electronique"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/professeur\/1586","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/professeur"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/professeur"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1587"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1586"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"categorie-equipe","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categorie-equipe?post=1586"},{"taxonomy":"departement-equipe","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/departement-equipe?post=1586"},{"taxonomy":"specialite-equipe","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/specialite-equipe?post=1586"},{"taxonomy":"etiquette-interne","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/etiquette-interne?post=1586"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}